{"tid":1554821,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我有病而公安打到我爆晒缸。。。","createTime":"2019-09-09T06:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T07:20:38.000Z","uid":267208,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"76e1897c52905fdf929afd2651146f7947b0637a","tid":1554821,"uid":267208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:30:56.000Z","msg":"有樣嘢我諗咗好耐<br />\n一路會諗可能自己諗多咗<br />\n但係尋晚有個朋友打俾我<br />\n原來佢諗嘅嘢同我一樣<br />\n咁可能唔係我諗多咗<br />\n<br />\n如果我有某種可以經血液傳播嘅病<br />\n而我又俾公安打到爆晒缸<br />\n咁個公安呢排又攰又抵抗力差<br />\n佢就算比我惹到都未必咁快有病徵<br />\n喺佢唔知情嘅情況又唔覺意傳咗俾佢屋企人<br />\n咁咪一傳十、十傳百？<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想製造恐慌或者鼓吹欺凌<br />\n只係一個genuine concern<br />\n<br />\n有無medical professionals可以解答？"},{"pid":"2d25771bdfb3c891c20c5a6d6b274f366e4722bd","tid":1554821,"uid":317299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:32:33.000Z","msg":"【913 八月十五】 金鐘悼義士<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554687</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XySvw4Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXySvw4Z.jpg&h=8251e762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hqGL5pZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhqGL5pZ.jpg&h=af6e3036&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c991563f068ccd360b37e69c4d4c4e7761a82ae","tid":1554821,"uid":267208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T07:20:38.000Z","msg":"有無人可以解答吓？"}]}